<title>tsbyḥ ygẖmr ạ̉rạḍynạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (tsbyḥ ygẖmr ạ̉rạḍynạ .. wrạyạt fwq ạlạ̉kạdẖyb
 wʿdk qwẗ btḥmynạ .. wjrạḥ ktyr btṭyb)2
 1- (mn ạllʿnẗ btkẖrj brkẗ .. wḥṣạd bʿd ạljfạf
 mn bʿd ạlḥzn frḥẗ .. tḥyy qlwb ạlḍʿạf)2
 2- (ydk jwh ạlạ̉kẖṭạr .. wmrạḥm llmḥtạj
 wqlwb klhyb mn nạr .. tnhḍ wsṭ ạlạ̉mwạj)2
 3- (fy̱ ạlbḥr ysẖq ṭryq .. ạ̉nhạr tgẖmr hḍạb
 slṭạn yrfʿ mn ạlḍyq .. wyrd snyn gẖyạb)2</lyrics>
</song>